.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_VERSION_AT_LEAST 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_version_at_least
.Nd compare XDnD protocol versions
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft Bool
.Fn x11dnd_version_at_least "int negotiated" "int required"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_version_at_least
returns
.Dv True
if
.Fa negotiated
is greater than or equal to
.Fa required ,
and
.Dv False
otherwise.
.Pp
Use this to check whether a peer's reported XDnD version meets a
minimum requirement before using protocol features that depend on a
specific version.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
.Dv True
if
.Fa negotiated No >= Fa required ,
.Dv False
otherwise.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_get_aware_version 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
